sub_title: Graduate in MSc Clinical Neuropsychology and an aspiring creative
summary:
An aspiring creative with a background in clinical neuropsychology. Currently looking for opportunities to combine my passion for photography and research, with a particular interest in creative production or marketing. 

An experienced research assistant with a demonstrated history of working in the hospital & health care industry. Skilled in academic writing, data collection, statistics, and data analytics. A freelance photographer and a creator on the side. Experienced in shooting weddings, festivals, concerts, and portraits. Lightroom and Photoshop are my go-to.
